---
 // Contact section component
---

<section id="contact" class="py-20 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-yellow-400">Contactame</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Me entusiasma la oportunidad de asumir nuevos desaf√≠os y aportar mi
          experiencia como desarrollador. Listo para trabajar y abierto a nuevas
          oportunidades, quedo atento a tu contacto.
        </p>
      </div>

      <form
        action="https://formspree.io/f/mkgqqlbp"
        method="POST"
        class="space-y-6"
      >
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div>
            <label for="name" class="block text-white mb-2 text-sm">Nombre</label>
            <input
              type="text"
              id="name"
              name="name"
              placeholder="Tim Berners-Lee..."
              required
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-transparent border border-gray-600 rounded-lg text-white placeholder-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:border-[#a8ff60] transition-colors"
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="email" class="block text-white mb-2 text-sm">Email</label>
            <input
              type="email"
              id="email"
              name="email"
              placeholder="timb@email.com"
              required
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-transparent border border-gray-600 rounded-lg text-white placeholder-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:border-[#a8ff60] transition-colors"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="message" class="block text-white mb-2 text-sm">Mensaje</label>
          <textarea
            id="message"
            name="message"
            rows="5"
            placeholder="I'm interested in working with you..."
            required
            class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-transparent border border-gray-600 rounded-lg text-white placeholder-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:border-[#a8ff60] transition-colors resize-none"
          ></textarea>
        </div>

        <button
          type="submit"
          class="px-8 py-3 border-2 border-white text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-white hover:text-[#1a1a1a] transition-all duration-300 font-medium"
        >
          Enviar mensaje
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
